metadata.name: The artist
metadata.description:
Like everything else, art evolves as well.
The old patterns and processes may still be sufficient, but in the 21st century, slowly it is not enough to show.
It is magnificent to create something in which the viewer gets lost and returns with a new experience.
That's why this work was born.
To remind.
A slightly different visual representation of a change.
Change between artist and artist, when the feeling of enlightenment comes - looking back for a moment above shoulder - a flash of thought would pull mind back, but won't let it and goes to a higher level

2048x2048
